 <div id="outline-container-org1aba1ce" class="outline-2">
 <h2 id="org1aba1ce">Usage</h2>
 <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org1aba1ce">
 <p>
Select four control points on the picture. When processed, the picture will be
transformed so that the four control points become the corners of an
axis-aligned rectangle.
</p>
</div>
</div>

 <div id="outline-container-org01be018" class="outline-2">
 <h2 id="org01be018">Installation</h2>
 <div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org01be018">
 <p>
It should run out of the box on most Unix-based systems.
</p>

 <p>
Fetch the  <a href="http://gitlab.com/ambrevar/perspector">source code</a> and read the  <code>README</code> file for further instructions.
</p>
</div>
</div>

